  "description_snippet": "**VULNERABILITY DETAILS**   \nThe javascript generated by ImageFetchTabHelper::GetImageDataByJs is unsafely created using the following format string.  \n  \nstd::string js =  \n    base::StringPrintf(\"__gCrWeb.imageFetch.getImageData(%d, '%s')\", call_id_,  \n                       url.spec().c_str());"
